<p>Visitors are welcome to visit Kolkata Police Head Quarters(Lalbazar) for any sorts of query related to Police. They may contact (Enquiry section at the Main Entrance Gate) to be guided to the appropriate department.
<p>In such circumstances please contact your local Police Station or sent us an e-mail.</p>
